  -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.questNameRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questName->最终选拔</li>
    <li>questName->狭雾山试炼</li>
    <li>questName->反击之刻</li>
    <li>questName->七日生存</li>
    <li>questName->鬼杀试炼</li>
    </AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.questNameRules.rulesStrings>
  <!-- EN: Demon Slayer Corps Guide Arrived -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ShuttleDelay.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>鬼杀队引路人已抵达</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ShuttleDelay.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: A veteran of the Demon Slayer Corps has arrived to escort your colonists to Mount Sagiri. Their haori bears the Corps' symbol, and their eyes hold the weight of countless battles.\n\n"Seven nights among demons. Send one to three candidates. Those who survive join our ranks. Those who fall become demon feast."\n\nChoose wisely - combat skills and physical toughness improve survival odds, while frailty makes the trial far more perilous.\n\nIMPORTANT: Colonists with demon blood CANNOT participate. The wisteria barriers surrounding Mount Sagiri are lethal to demons. -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ShuttleDelay.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>一位资深鬼杀队士前来接送你的殖民者前往狭雾山。他的羽织印有鬼杀队的标志，眼神背负了无数战斗带来的沉重。\n\n“七晚与鬼为伍，选出一到三名应试者吧。生者为队士，败者为鬼飧。”\n\n谨慎选择⸺格斗技能和体质能提高生存率，而体弱者会在试炼面临更大的危机。\n\n重要提醒: 拥有鬼之血的殖民者不得参加，因为狭雾山周围的紫藤花林对鬼是致命的。</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ShuttleDelay.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Final Selection Results -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>最终选拔结果</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The transport has returned from Mount Sagiri. The survival rolls have been made, and fates have been decided... -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>运输舱已从狭雾山返回。已完成生存判定，而他们的命运也尘埃落定……</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Final Selection Rewards -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.DropPods.customLetterLabel.slateRef>最终选拔奖励</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.DropPods.customLetterLabel.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Rewards from the Final Selection have arrived via transport pod. -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.DropPods.customLetterText.slateRef>最终选拔的奖励已经由运输舱送达。</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.DropPods.customLetterText.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Final Selection - Total Failure -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsDied.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>最终选拔 ⸺ 全军复没</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsDied.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: No one has returned from Mount Sagiri. The demons have claimed all who entered. Their sacrifice will not be forgotten, but the Corps gains no new members this day. -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsDied.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>没有人从狭雾山回来。鬼抓走了所有进入山中的参加者。虽然他们的牺牲永远不会被忘记，但鬼杀队一个新成员都没有增加。</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsDied.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  
